Monster from Bikini Beach (2008 - USA)

Comedy / Horror
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1332028/


TFO (Trash Film Orgy) Productions

Monster from Bikini Beach has several simultaneous and interrelated plots. The first is the Go-Go-a-Thon that has the whole town buzzing, be-bopping and scattin' around in as little clothing as possible. Meanwhile, a salty detective gone bad is on the hunt for a lost drug cache that could set him up to live out his golden years in the company of his ditzy but beautiful girl Boom Boom in some far away and tropical locale. Everybody's plans, however, are threatened by the emergence of the beast, a primordial creature from the depths of the river that is vicious, ugly, murderous, and apparently horny.
